OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe low
OL,6,Fcloud around the North Sea coast will
OL,7,Fmove inland into eastern parts. It
OL,8,Fwill stay dry with mainly clear skies
OL,9,Fthrough Dumfries and Galloway. Winds
OL,10,Fremaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny low cloud should clear
OL,13,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,14,Fsunny spells developing. Temperatures
OL,15,Fdown a bit, but still warm in any
OL,16,Fsunshine, especially the southwest.
OL,17,FLight northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
