OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and settled with bright and sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Temperatures around normal,
OL,8,Ffeeling warm or very warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine. Some cloudier periods
OL,10,Fexpected.
